{"TopicId":52440,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"PIC HEAVY - Lifting Body Aircraft (wingless)","CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-09T05:17:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-09T05:17:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELOTS OF ALT - F12 PART CLIPPING!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe X-24 Lifting Body\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/w1qac5b0fcuyu9d/X-24%20Lifting%20Body.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/w1qac5b0fcuyu9d/X-24%20Lifting%20Body.craft\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/btB1sN3.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022btB1sN3.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis Plane is a model off the real life Martin Marietta X-24 experimental plane \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Marietta_X-24A\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Csub\u003Ehttp://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martin_Marietta_X-24A\u003C/sub\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECareful on landing this sucker \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E if it tips over, it will quite literally blow itself apart due to all the pieces inside...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/e4lWa33.png\u0022 alt=\u0022e4lWa33.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/VvGELY7.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022VvGELY7.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ADwAWjr.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ADwAWjr.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XTxS8Qo.png\u0022 alt=\u0022XTxS8Qo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHave fun! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ep.s. Whoever it was that posted the forum asking for this thank you \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GusTurbo","CreatedById":57552,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-09T05:50:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPretty cool. Any plans for a space version?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-09T06:08:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI could if you want \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAll it\u0027d need is to replace 2 tanks with space fuel, add a rocket engine, and internal airhog to the max...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027d probably be un-landable with all the weight though. Unless I added more lift...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWell, its worth a try!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GusTurbo","CreatedById":57552,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-09T20:06:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EQuestion: how do you land this craft? Without any lift, it seems like it would be difficult to come in at a shallow enough angle.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-10T02:18:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s actually impossible to build a plane in KSP without any wings due to mechanics of drag vs. lift (only wings have \u0022lift\u0022 everything else has drag to my understanding). This one has its wings INSIDE it. Soooooooooo technically its not a true \u0022lifting body\u0022 aircraft but its as close as it can get! And its just about as close to the actual aircraft as I\u0027m willing to try \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-11-10T05:03:32Z\u0022 title=\u002211/10/2013 05:03  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 10, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Avera9eJoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}